'''Emmett Gene Hendricks''' (February 14, 1938 – May 18, 2003) was an American [[college basketball]] coach. He was the head coach of the [[Louisiana Tech Bulldogs basketball]] program from 1974–1977. In 2003, Hendricks died at the age of 65 after a lengthy illness.

